Well school has started and everything is cool and dandy. Been hanging out with everyone and its cool. Drama has sorta started and when I went into the theatre for the first practice it was like O MY GOD ITS FUCKIN AWESOME. So yah I can't wait for the next play. Other then that I havent been doing anything besides sitting here and being bored >_>. Its boring day after boring day. But atleast tommorrow might get to hang out and PARTY WOOOO not really party but w/e. I'm a little meh about Homecomming idk but right now its a meh. I dont think i have anything else to write.

well i had one of the best days of my life yesterday. Miranda, Kevin and my parents planned a surprise b-day party for me and it was so much fun with the karioke(sp) and hot tubbin and everything. Before i get into everything i need to apologize to Miranda for being a jerk all week. Im sorry Miranda. Ok now yesterday i went to red robin with Kevin Miranda and Dan then we went to Media Play and i got Warped tour 2005 and an Empire Strikes Back poster (star wars) and media play has the most comfertible(sp) chairs and couches anywhere. Then after that we went to Dicks sporting goods. Played tennis and then Dan nailed a tennis ball then ran the Miranda got mad at Dan for not going to get the tennis ball. Then we got back to my house and SURPRISE. A lot of people were there and we were kariokein( major sp) and ppl got in the hot tub and Kevins friends dumped me in the pool and my phone was in my pocket so it got wet and short circuted and now its dead so i get a new phone YAY. Today really diddnt do anything but get the sims 2 and it takes so long to load in my computer that i cleaned my room as it was loading so now i have a clean room and all that stuff. Well it was a great day with everyone yesterday and another sorry to Miranda :-D Untill next time

Well the summer has been really boring really haven't done anything. I started and finished drivers training and got my permit so stay off the sidewalks. I went and seen my cousin who i haven't seen in about 3 years and hat had to be the highlight of the summer next to Danielle's b-day party. I got the computer in my room so thats really all I have been doing. All this boredom really makes me want school so i'm extremly deperate >_> Well thats all till next time.

Well this past week was another BORING summer vacation week. I really diddn't do anything till Wednesday when me and Dan worked out asses off. We got 50 bucks for it so i guess it was worth it. On Thursday I had to do some more yard work. On Friday I went to the Carnival with Jennifer, Brett and Dan wasted A LOT of money there about 60 bucks. Later that day me and Dan went to the fireworks and Miranda called me and said to meet her by the entrance so we walked to the other side of the park to get her then she wanted a candy apple so we went a got one then the fireworks started so we said we had to go but she said she couldn't walk back alone so we walked all the way to her parents then all the way back to where we were sitting the fireworks were ok but they weren't great. Then on Saturday went back to the carnival and rode a few rides. It was fun. Today really diddnt do anything except sit in the hot tub =) I forgot to say I got a hot tub WOO HOO. Well that was my week.
